OL,3,CUS journalist Evan Gershkovich appears
OL,4,Cat closed-door trial in Russia
OL,6,FWall Street Journal reporter Evan
OL,7,FGershkovich has appeared at a closed-
OL,8,Fdoor trial in Russia on espionage
OL,9,Fcharges.
OL,11,FMr Gershkovich, 32, was arrested 15
OL,12,Fmonths ago when he was on a reporting
OL,13,Ftrip to the Ural Mountains city. He is
OL,14,Fthe first Western journalist to be
OL,15,Farrested on espionage charges in post-
OL,16,FSoviet Russia.
