OL,3,CUS journalist Evan Gershkovich appears
OL,4,Cat closed-door trial in Russia
OL,6,FThe 32-year-old appeared in the
OL,7,Fcourtroom on Wednesday morning in a
OL,8,Fglass cage, with his head shaven clean
OL,9,Fand wearing a black-and-blue plaid
OL,10,Fshirt.
OL,12,FHe faces up to 20 years in prison if
OL,13,Fthe court finds him guilty.
OL,15,FThe Russian authorities claimed he was
OL,16,Fgathering secret information for the
OL,17,FUS intelligence. Mr Gershkovich, the
OL,18,FWall Street Journal and the US
OL,19,Fgovernment vigorously deny the
OL,20,Fallegations.
