OL,3,CUS journalist Evan Gershkovich appears
OL,4,Cat closed-door trial in Russia
OL,6,FAfter his arrest on March 29, 2023, Mr
OL,7,FGershkovich was held in Moscow's
OL,8,FLefortovo Prison. He has appeared
OL,9,Fhealthy during court hearings in which
OL,10,Fhis appeals for release have been
OL,11,Frejected.
OL,13,FRussian courts convict more than 99%
OL,14,Fof the defendants who come before
OL,15,Fthem. Prosecutors can appeal sentences
OL,16,Fthat they regard as too lenient and
OL,17,Feven can appeal acquittals.
