OL,3,CUS journalist Evan Gershkovich appears
OL,4,Cat closed-door trial in Russia
OL,6,FMr Gershkovich's arrest came about a
OL,7,Fyear after President Vladimir Putin
OL,8,Fpushed through laws that criminalised
OL,9,Fpress criticism of the war in Ukraine
OL,10,Fand making statements seen as
OL,11,Fdiscrediting the military.
OL,13,FThere have been accusations that
OL,14,FRussia is targeting Americans as
OL,15,Fanimosity between Moscow and
OL,16,FWashington grew.
